{"id":556284,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/04/北大飞-奥巴马女儿因抽大麻被哈佛开除？-过/","date":"2017-04-11T07:53:38Z","modified":"2017-04-11T07:53:38Z","title":"北大飞 | 奥巴马女儿因抽大麻被哈佛开除？——过分弱智的谣言","content":"<p>要是您在哪儿看见谁在传这谣言，请把这篇文章扔进去，当场打脸。</p>\n<p>最近在不止一处看见微信里开始疯传这么一则消息。说是奥巴马女儿因为抽大麻被哈佛开除。还附有有关英文网站截图。</p>\n<p>感谢朋友彭纳提供下面造谣现场截图：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/640B1QWPWZN.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-556285\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/640B1QWPWZN.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/640B1QWPWZN.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/640B1QWPWZN-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/640B1QWPWZN-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/640RSPIX42I.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-556286\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/640RSPIX42I.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/640RSPIX42I.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/640RSPIX42I-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/640RSPIX42I-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>于是各路川粉又开始high了。</p>\n<p>只不过这是个非常弱智的谣言。如果你在英文谷歌上搜索这一消息，首先出现的就是著名辟谣网站snopes.com的辟谣。为方便大家传播，下面是个简单总结，说明这一谣言的来龙去脉。点击文末的“原文链接”看snopes原文。</p>\n<p>1. 这个“消息”最初来自网站&#8221;last line of defense&#8221;（最后一道防线）。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/640ULR1B881.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-556287\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/640ULR1B881.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"365\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/640ULR1B881.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/640ULR1B881-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>2. 但问题在于，这个网站是个专门登载愚人节新闻的搞笑娱乐网站。人家早就给了免责声明：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/64011W6X3NW.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-556288\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/64011W6X3NW.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"83\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/64011W6X3NW.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/64011W6X3NW-300x45.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><em>The Resistance may include information from sources that may or may not be reliable and facts that don’t necessarily exist. All articles should be considered satirical and any and all quotes attributed to actual people complete and total baloney. Pictures that represent actual people should be considered altered and not in any way real.</em></p>\n<div id=\"js_article\" class=\"rich_media\">\n<div class=\"rich_media_inner\">\n<div id=\"page-content\">\n<div id=\"img-content\" class=\"rich_media_area_primary\">\n<div id=\"js_content\" class=\"rich_media_content \">\n<section>\n<section>\n<section>\n<section><em><br />\n翻译： 本网站可能含有来源未必可靠的信息及并不存在的事实。所有文章均应被视为讽刺，所有对实际人物的引用都是扯淡。所有显示实际人物的照片都应被认为ps过，完全不真实。<br />\n</em></p>\n<p>OK。满意了吗？还不满意？再看看下面这件事：</p>\n<p>3. 奥巴马的女儿虽然已被哈佛录取，但她向学校申请了&#8221;gap year&#8221;，即推迟一年入学（原因应该是跟随父亲参加各种活动之类，但已经有人造谣说因为她怀孕了，所以这里先提个醒）。所以直到2017年秋天她才会正式成为哈佛的学生。还没入学就被开除？想太多了。</p>\n<p>再重复一遍，要是您在哪儿看见谁在传这谣言，请赶紧把这篇文章扔进去。谢谢了。</p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,9203],"tags":[22930,9420,8823,26025,10722,15083]}